PutMultiple(ReadOnlySpan<Byte>, ReadOnlySpan<Byte>, ref Int32)

Store multiple contiguous data elements by cursor. This is only valid for FixedMultiValueDatabase instances (they are opened with DuplicatesFixed flag). The cursor is positioned at the new item, or on failure usually near it. Note: Earlier documentation incorrectly said errors would leave the state of the cursor unchanged.
